            Ensure maximum profit streams by utilizing statistical analysis
            tools to see ways you can improve.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- profit, Third card -->

      <div class="text-center col-lg-4">
        <div class="card card-extra">
          <i class="card-icon fa-solid fa-coins fa-5x"></i>
          <p class="feature-box-p">
